      "left": "",
      "text": "ואתי כולה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כר' ישמעאל ולאו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אדרבי יוחנן קפריך וזה הפירוש",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נראה יותר דמסברא אין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לנו למעט אכלתי ולא אכלתי ממלקות כדי להקשות לר' יוחנן ומשני מסתברא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כו' והוא הדין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דה\"מ לשנויי דניחא ליה לאוקומה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כר\"ע דכולהו סתמי כוותיה <big><b>היכן מצינו.</b></big> ואע\"ג דבמפרש כל שהוא חייב כדאמר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בגמרא סתמא דמילתא דעתו אסתם אכילות",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שבתורה <big><b>היכן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מצינו</b></big>. הלכך כיון",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דחמיר דעתו אכל שהוא <big><b>כרבי שמעון</b></big>. ר' יוחנן דאית ליה בפרק בתרא דיומא (<a href=\"/yoma/74a\">דף עד.</a>) דחצי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שיעור אסור מן התורה אתי שפיר כרבנן דבחצי שיעור ליכא מלקות אלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "איסור בעלמא ובסוף פרק",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "גיד הנשה (<a href=\"/chullin/98a\">חולין צח.</a>) מוכח בהדיא דכרבנן סבירא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ליה ובפרק אלו עוברין (<a href=\"/pesachim/43b\">פסחים מג:</a>) קאמר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "רבי יוחנן דבכל התורה אין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "היתר מצטרף לאיסור",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חוץ מאיסורי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נזיר ואי כל שהוא למכות למה לי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "צירוף <big><b>ולא אמרו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כזית</b></big>. ודוקא בשאר איסור בעינן כזית",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לקרבן שהקרבן תלוי בכרת וזדונו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בכרת לא הוי אלא בכזית אבל בשבועת בטוי דאין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בו כרת אלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לאו והקרבן תלוי בלאו כי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "היכי דלוקין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אכל שהוא מביא קרבן אכל שהוא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<big><b>ואי ס\"ד</b></big>.",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "תימה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דלמא שאני",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הכא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דגלי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קרא כדדרשינן באלו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עוברין (פסחים דף",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מג: ושם) ובפ' ג' מינים (נזיר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לה:) ממשרת וכל",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משרת וי\"ל דאי סבירא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ליה כר\"ש הוה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מוקי ליה לקרא למילתא אחריתי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 21b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    }
  ]
}